Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:17.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hello, welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.81,0:06:17.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\c&HB7D2DC&}Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:20.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, a large ramen again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:25.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This customer's been coming here for breakfast,\Nlunch and dinner for the last three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.03,0:06:26.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Where on Earth does he live?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:30.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:33.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\c&HD2D2DE&\3c&H7372F1&\fs36\bord3\fnArial\be2\pos(361.399,91)}Open 24 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.16,0:06:33.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\b0\c&H807D86&\3c&H232655&\fs28\pos(365.93,210)}Ramen
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.54,0:06:38.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He doesn't have any problems paying\Nand is well-mannered,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.21,0:06:39.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but I wonder which country he's from?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:48.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.38,0:06:49.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:52.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How can we get out of here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.18,0:06:57.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's already been four days since\Nwe wandered into the thick woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:06:58.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Everyone has now gotten completely worn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:02.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even Hayashida, who's always energetic,\Nis in this condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:06.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's no life in Hokuto's face either.\NAnd Freddie...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.24,0:07:08.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,A naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.57,0:07:12.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, calm down. Think carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:14.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why is a naruto stuck to Freddie's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:18.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's right! It means that\Nthere's some food in this forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.83,0:07:23.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And we all split up to search for food.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.54,0:07:25.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What did we find?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:27.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In the end, this is all we could find.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:30.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then where did Freddie get the naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.63,0:07:31.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.43,0:07:33.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, there are many mysteries in thick woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:36.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, where did Hayashida go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.18,0:07:37.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's been almost five hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.47,0:07:39.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.44,0:07:43.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.69,0:07:44.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:46.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hayashida! You're all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.69,0:07:51.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I bought these at a convenience store.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:54.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I guess convenience stores\N really are everywhere, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.45,0:07:57.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I walked an animal trail\Nfor at least three hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.58,0:08:00.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wow, that must've been a lot of work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.12,0:08:01.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hayashida...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If you got to a convenience store,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:06.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,shouldn't you have just asked for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:08.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We're all close friends, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can't go alone, leaving you guys behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:14.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So I rushed back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.34,0:08:15.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hayashida...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:16.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I love you, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:18.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, that's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:21.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,By the way, Hayashida,\NI'm sure you didn't, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.31,0:08:22.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.73,0:08:23.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Where's the hot water?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:24.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh! I forgot it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:27.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Geez! How could you forget\Nsomething so important?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:29.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are you really trying to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:30.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We're gonna starve to death, aren't we?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.65,0:08:32.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's not the issue here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.24,0:08:34.70,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,820)\pos(339.873,100)\c&H5584D4&\shad0\fs50\frz4\frx10\fry356\fnAveria Sans}Joshua Tree
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:35.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The fifth day since we entered the thick woods...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:36.24,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,0)\pos(362.532,390)\be2\fs34}Day 5
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:39.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've already lost my hopes and dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Hayashida?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.75,0:08:45.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wasn't our dream that we were\Nto go to Koshien to play baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.67,0:08:49.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're right! We came here to play baseball!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:53.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's right! Even if we're in the thick woods,\Nif we give up our dream, that means we lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.51,0:08:54.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We should play baseball!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.59,0:08:55.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.68,0:08:56.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:57.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.76,0:08:58.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:01.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:03.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't hit the ball hard in the thick woods!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:05.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We've only got one ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.69,0:09:07.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll go and get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\c&HD2D2DE&\3c&H7372F1&\fs42\fscx111.025\bord3\fnArial\frz357.897\frx2\fry4\be2\pos(225.449,177)}Open 24 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:13.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnArial Black\b0\c&H647862&\3c&H232655&\fs43\frx6\fry14\frz359.437\pos(224.316,240)}Ramen
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.36,0:09:13.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,A man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:16.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:17.53,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Get that ball over there for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:18.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.37,0:09:21.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Five hours later, Hayashida came back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:25.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So I was able to meet a very kind pops\Nwho owns a ramen restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.71,0:09:29.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I guess things aren't really that bad in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:32.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you ask that pops for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.96,0:09:34.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh! That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.84,0:09:36.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I just panicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.88,0:09:39.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Looking for a ball calmly\Nis more abnormal than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.14,0:09:41.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Look at the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:46.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Birds are flying freely,\Nas if they're laughing at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:53.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wild animals have nothing to fear, no matter if\Nthey're in thick woods like this or anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.57,0:09:58.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Speaking of animals,\N we had a gorilla on our team, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:00.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:01.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:03.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The gorilla's beckoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.16,0:10:04.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But can we trust him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:05.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.91,0:10:07.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's go follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:11.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But he walks fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't lose him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:14.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.92,0:10:17.13,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's climbing the tree and\Nlooking around the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.13,0:10:19.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Just as you'd expect from a gorilla.\NHe does things differently!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.80,0:10:22.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's starting to look dependable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:25.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And after three hours \Nof wandering around in the thick woods...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:29.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Is this path really the correct one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.06,0:10:32.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Lights!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake!\NThose are lights from a city!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.61,0:10:35.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.48,0:10:37.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:40.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thanks, gorilla. It's all thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is a different gorilla!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.45,0:10:44.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then where's our gorilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.99,0:10:50.00,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fs34\c&HFF6780&\pos(350,465)}Previous gorilla that got lost
