Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:36.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:38.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.34,0:11:40.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The next episode is... The next episode is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.84,0:11:42.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, you don't intend\Nto do the preview, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What are you saying, Hayashida?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:48.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(22.658,465)}Dejiko has come to \NCromartie High School, nyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:49.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(113.291,465)}Dejiko...
